Use normal Astro/MDX component props. Numeric values need `{...}` braces:

```mdx
<HopfBifurcation
  muMin={-0.5}
  muMax={1.8}
  cycleSeconds={12}
  domain={2.4}
  gridDensity={17}
  omega={1.4}
  particleSpawnRate={8}
  maxParticles={60}
  particleLifetime={9}
  particleRadius={2.5}
/>
```

In the current overview page, inside the grid, that would look like:

```mdx
<HopfBifurcation
  ariaLabel="Animated supercritical Hopf bifurcation..."
  muMin={-0.5}
  muMax={1.8}
  cycleSeconds={12}
  domain={2.4}
  gridDensity={17}
  omega={1.4}
/>
```

Avoid string syntax like:

```mdx
muMin="-0.5"
```

Use:

```mdx
muMin={-0.5}
```
